[normal]              
[normal]Professional workers, trained and certifiably competent to national standard, assist actual or intending
[normal] us
[normal]er
[normal]s
[normal], issue tickets from booking offices which machines can’t, assist t
[normal]hose for whom the internet is a
[normal] nightmare.  Some transactions can only 
[normal]be at ticket offices – 
[normal]Senior Citizen or other rai
[normal]lcards
[normal] 
[normal]are 
[normal]not accepted by 
[normal]every
[normal] TVM; refunds can only be at a ticket office or by 
[normal]post;
[normal] using compensation vouchers issued for late or cancelled trains can only be 
[normal]at
[normal] a face-to-face 
[normal]site
[normal].  UK booking offices access 
[normal]Eurostar
[normal] ticketing, hardly any TVMs can.
